{"type":"text","timestamp":1775845130581,"sessionID":"ses_28763aefaffeXLHE2Fqv4IE2z2","part":{"id":"prt_d789d9be6001IwmN8cmLnibz55","messageID":"msg_d789d91f5001fKepP8JrryyM1h","sessionID":"ses_28763aefaffeXLHE2Fqv4IE2z2","type":"text","text":"Now let me create a comprehensive verification report:\n\n## AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Verification Report\n\n### Executive Summary\n\n**Status**: ❌ **NOT COMPLIANT** - Critical gaps between spec and implementation\n\n**Compliance Score**: ~35%\n\n---\n\n### 1. Spec Requirements vs Implementation\n\n#### 1.1 Client-Go Typed Client (Required by Spec)\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n- No `client-go/` directory exists\n- No typed client code generated\n- Code uses `dynamic.Interface` instead (handlers at `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go:18-20`)\n- **Gap**: Missing entire client-go infrastructure\n\n---\n\n#### 1.2 Informer Types\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n    Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n    Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ❌ **BUILD ERROR**\n\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:67` references `runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:75` references `runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInformer`\n- **Build Error**: `undefined: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer`\n\n---\n\n#### 1.3 Lister Interfaces\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n    AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ⚠️ **PARTIAL**\n\nCustom implementation at `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor.go:56-67`:\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n    Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Gaps**:\n- Missing `List(selector labels.Selector)` method\n- Missing expansion interfaces\n\n---\n\n#### 1.4 Sandbox Deletion (AR-006 Core Requirement)\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`changes/AR-006/proposal.md`):\n```go\nfunc (p *SandboxProcessor) Delete(\n    ctx context.Context,\n    sandboxName string,\n    namespace string,\n    options *DeleteOptions,\n) error\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n- No `Delete()` method in `SandboxProcessor`\n- Only internal `rollback()` method exists (`sandbox_processor.go:469-473`)\n- No sandbox deletion endpoint in handlers\n- No lifecycle management implementation\n\n---\n\n#### 1.5 Lifecycle Management\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`changes/AR-006/proposal.md`):\n\nRequired components:\n1. `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_lifecycle.go` - Lifecycle Manager\n2. `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_finalizer.go` - Finalizer Controller\n3. `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_cleanup.go` - Cleanup Orchestrator\n4. `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/idle_timeout.go` - Idle Timeout Handler\n\n**Implementation Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n- None of the required files exist\n- No lifecycle phase management\n- No finalizer implementation\n- No idle timeout monitoring\n\n---\n\n#### 1.6 API Endpoints\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`changes/AR-006/proposal.md`):\n\n| Method | Path | Status |\n|--------|------|--------|\n| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/{name}` | ✅ Exists (handler only, no sandbox cleanup) |\n| `DELETE` | `/v1/sandboxes/{name}` | ❌ Missing |\n| `GET` | `/v1/sandboxes/{name}/status` | ❌ Missing |\n| `POST` | `/v1/sandboxes/{name}/extend` | ❌ Missing |\n\n**Current Implementation**:\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go:195-216` - `DeleteAgentRuntime` exists but only deletes CR, no sandbox cleanup\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox.go` - No delete handler\n\n---\n\n#### 1.7 REST Resource Plurals\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n- AgentRuntime: `agentruntimes`\n- CodeInterpreter: `codeinterpreters`\n\n**Implementation Status**: ✅ **CORRECT**\n\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go:24` uses `\"agentruntimes\"`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter.go:23` uses `\"codeinterpreters\"`\n\n---\n\n### 2. Build Status\n\n**Status**: ❌ **FAILING**\n\n```bash\npkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:67:27: undefined: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer\npkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:75:27: undefined: runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInformer\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Test Results\n\n**Status**: ⚠️ **PARTIAL**\n\nHandler tests pass (tested via dynamic client):\n- ✅ `TestDeleteAgentRuntime_Success`\n- ✅ `TestDeleteAgentRuntime_NotFound`\n- ✅ `TestDeleteCodeInterpreter_Success`\n- ✅ `TestDeleteCodeInterpreter_NotFound`\n\n**Gaps**:\n- ❌ No sandbox processor delete tests\n- ❌ No lifecycle management tests\n- ❌ No finalizer tests\n- ❌ No idle timeout tests\n- ❌ No integration tests for cascading deletion\n\n---\n\n### 4. Critical Issues\n\n| Issue | Severity | Impact |\n|-------|----------|--------|\n| Build failures | 🔴 Critical | Code does not compile |\n| Missing client-go | 🔴 Critical | No type-safe Kubernetes client |\n| No sandbox deletion | 🔴 Critical | Core AR-006 feature missing |\n| No lifecycle management | 🔴 Critical | No phase tracking or state machine |\n| No finalizer implementation | 🔴 Critical | Resource leaks possible |\n| No idle timeout | 🟠 High | Resource waste in production |\n| Incomplete lister interfaces | 🟡 Medium | Cannot list with selectors |\n\n---\n\n### 5. Recommendations\n\n#### P0 (Immediate - Blocking)\n1. **Fix build errors**: Remove or define informer interfaces in `routes.go`\n2. **Generate client-go code**: Run `make gen-client` or create manually\n3. **Implement SandboxProcessor.Delete()**: Core deletion logic with graceful shutdown\n\n#### P1 (Short-term)\n4. **Add sandbox deletion endpoint**: `DELETE /v1/sandboxes/{name}`\n5. **Implement finalizer pattern**: Prevent resource leaks\n6. **Add lifecycle phase tracking**: Pending → Running → Terminating → Terminated\n7. **Implement cascading deletion**: Pod → Services → Claims\n\n#### P2 (Long-term)\n8. **Implement idle timeout monitoring**: Auto-shutdown idle sandboxes\n9. **Add status endpoint**: `GET /v1/sandboxes/{name}/status`\n10. **Add force delete option**: Emergency cleanup bypass\n11. **Write integration tests**: End-to-end deletion verification\n\n---\n\n### 6. Compliance Matrix\n\n| Requirement | Status | Location |\n|-------------|--------|----------|\n| Clientset Interface | ❌ | Missing |\n| Typed Client (AgentRuntime) | ❌ | Missing |\n| Typed Client (CodeInterpreter) | ❌ | Missing |\n| Informer Factory | ❌ | Missing |\n| Lister (with List method) | ⚠️ | Partial (`sandbox_processor.go:56-67`) |\n| Expansion Interfaces | ❌ | Missing |\n| SandboxProcessor.Delete() | ❌ | Missing |\n| Lifecycle Manager | ❌ | Missing |\n| Finalizer Controller | ❌ | Missing |\n| Cleanup Orchestrator | ❌ | Missing |\n| Idle Timeout Handler | ❌ | Missing |\n| DELETE /api/v1/agentruntimes/{name} | ✅ | `agent_runtime.go:195` (no cleanup) |\n| DELETE /v1/sandboxes/{name} | ❌ | Missing |\n| Graceful Shutdown | ❌ | Missing |\n| Cascading Deletion | ❌ | Missing |\n| Phase Tracking | ❌ | Missing |\n\n---\n\n### Conclusion\n\n**The AR-006 implementation is NOT ready for review.**\n\nWhile basic CRUD handlers exist for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter (using dynamic client), the **core deletion and lifecycle management features are completely missing**. Additionally, the codebase has **build-breaking errors** due to undefined informer types.\n\n**Next Steps**:\n1. Fix build errors in `routes.go`\n2. Either generate client-go code or remove references to it\n3. Implement core `SandboxProcessor.Delete()` method\n4. Add deletion endpoint to sandbox handler\n5. Implement finalizer-based cleanup\n\nWould you like me to help fix these issues?","time":{"start":1775845130578,"end":1775845130578}}}
